SPOTON_LITE_DAEMON_CHILD_ECL_SUPPORTED

Automatically defined if the directory /usr/bin/ecl or if the
directory /usr/local/bin/ecl exists. A Common LISP implementation of
SHA-512 is included if one of the aforementioned directories exists.

SPOTON_LITE_DAEMON_DISABLE_SOME_STATISTICS

Not utilized.

SPOTON_LITE_DAEMON_DTLS_SUPPORTED

Enable if the system's Qt supports DTLS. Requires Qt 5.12.

SPOTON_LITE_DAEMON_ENABLE_IDENTITIES_CONTAINER

If enabled, remote identities are recorded in a memory-resident container.

SPOTON_LITE_DAEMON_IDENTITIES_CONTAINER_MAXIMUM_SIZE

Maximum size of memory-resident identities container.

SPOTON_LITE_DAEMON_OPENSSL_SUPPORTED

Defined if OpenSSL is supported.

SPOTON_LITE_DAEMON_SCHEDULING_ENABLED

Defined if /usr/include/sched.h exists. Supports process scheduling.

SPOTON_LITE_DAEMON_SHA_TEST

If enabled, test SHA-512.
